_aChangeLog.text: Fixed bug where player could hit !R at the end of the last stage and instantly beat the map
Fixed a skip halfway through the last stage
Added env_tonemap to fix map being extremely bright at some points
All delayed teleports changed to instantaneous
Packed only essential files into the .bsp
Reduced frequency and volume of helicopter sound (7-12>30-60) (0.6-0.4)
Made the env_sparks on the generators in level 2 not produce any sound
Fixed bug where the door frames would cast shadows where they shouldnt
Fixed a bug where one of the prop statics would cause the HDR lighting to glitch out (changed to dynamic)
Seams in 3D Skybox made as unnoticeable as possible (unable to sew)
